Invocation Name: stream sounds
des:
The soothing sound of a small stream.

Play the gentle and relaxing sound of a small stream flowing nearby. Guaranteed to help you relax or block out unwanted noises. Whether you call it a babbling brook, creek, or stream, you'll love the familiar riparian sound provided by Stream Sounds.
